>
> The gap is not subtle. It is obvious from a conversational distance. Every cushion cut engagement ring owner planning to add a wedding band must physically test the fit before purchasing — either with their actual ring at a jeweller or by ordering from a retailer with a return policy specifically to evaluate the pairing." — Farzana Hasan, **[Diamond Critics](https://diamondcritics.com/about-farzana/)**

